LVM means logical volume management
  here we can connect miltiple hard disk converted into one logical drive
  here we have 
  1. pv (physical volumes)
  to
  2. vg (volume group)
  to 
  3. lv (logical group)
  means we first neet to connect one physical multiple volumes pv having storage each disk 2gb we have 4 pv finally we got 8gb logical volumes
  here we can pattion the logical  volumes like  how much we need stotage for requirement like 2.8 gb or 5.5gb or 7.6gb
  here we can do saparate the storage
  
